			<title>Univention S4 Connector</title>
			<itemizedlist>
				<listitem><simpara>
					When objects are renamed in UCS update their DN in the group member mapping caches (<u:bug>47636</u:bug>).
				</simpara></listitem>
				<listitem><simpara>
